a guy i worked with painted at work and at home.  at home he never used a
respirator and at work only a 3m dual filtered mask.  he used to think it
was funny when we would look in the booth at him shaking our heads.  now
he's in a wheel chair for life due to it.  this is one of the reasons you
wont meet too many "old" body guys.
